  "name": "Morrison COU2 VAD Hemolysis CFD Credibility Assessment (NC-8 Clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The operating envelope is explicitly bounded (flow 1-7 L/min, rotational speed 2000-5000 RPM, hematocrit 35-45%) and validation experiments cover boundary and interior points of that envelope. All 13 credibility factors are assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel. Decision: Accepted.",
